# Problem
Training is too slow. I'm trying different strategies to optimize training times and increase sample efficiency

# Solution
I'm using multiple (4) asynchronous collectors. Since the batch size is still one (one experience step to one optimization step), the change won't be expressive, but at least there shouldn't be a great loss in performance.

# Results
Training it/s increased from ~60 to ~80. A small performance improvement. No loss in performance was observed